text: Lipovy Klyuch () is a rural locality (a village) in Verkhnebishindinsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 84 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 20 km from Tuymazy, 7 km from Verkhniye Bishindy. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Lipovy Klyuch
